data.description: Model-like home in highly desired Red River Ranch awaits you! An open and spacious floor plan with high ceilings welcomes you into this single story 4 bedroom + 2 full baths home.  The family room leads into a gorgeous kitchen with a large island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, built-in microwave and ample counterspace & cabinets for plenty of storage.  The large master suite with large windows for plenty of natural light has his and her sinks, a garden tub, separate shower and a spacious walk-in closet.  Two of the three large secondary bedrooms share a bathroom between them.  The third secondary bedroom is perfect for a guest suite, study or exercise room.  Modern and durable laminate flooring in all the main areas.  Relax on the covered patio in the large backyard.  Red River Ranch is conveniently located in fast growing Cibolo with easy access to major highways, Randolph AFB & Fort Sam Houston and only a few minutes from downtown with plenty of shopping and dining nearby.  Highly rated SCUISD schools! WELCOME HOME!
